<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3926865>
    dc:description "Figs 27–30. Raillietina mahnerti sp. nov. 27. a) Scolex. b) Sucker hooklets. c) Rostellar hook. 28. Mature proglottis, ventral view. 29. Copulatory organs. 30. Gravid proglottis with egg capsules. Scale bars: 27a, 28, 30 = 100 µm; 27b = 20 µm; 27c = 10 µm; 29 = 50 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3926865/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

